_string:
3. Processing time

sultan777.io stores your personal data as long as your account exists or as necessary for the operation of our Service. Even if you use the Service every few years when searching for, exchanging, selling or buying items, we will retain your personal data and your account until you close it. After you close your account, your personal data will be deleted, blocked or anonymized in accordance with applicable law, unless legal requirements or other prevailing legitimate purposes require longer retention. Sometimes it is impossible to completely delete data because of the need to comply with the consistency of exchange, sale and purchase on the trading platform.

If you use the right to object to the processing of your personal data, we will consider your objection and delete the data processed for the purpose objected, unless there is another legal basis for the processing and storage of this data or if the storage of this data is not required under applicable law.

If you withdraw your consent to the processing of your personal data or your child's data, we will delete the data to the extent that the collection and processing of data is based on the consent.

 

4. User right

Data protection laws in force in different territories grant rights with respect to your personal data.

To exercise your rights, you can contact us using the contact information specified on the website or through your personal account.

 

Right to information

You can apply for provision of a copy of your personal data by sending us a request in any way possible.

 

Right to rectification

You can change some of your personal data in your personal account, or contact us with a request to change or correct your data if they are inaccurate.

 

Right to be forgotten (“oblivion”)

You can request us to delete all or some of your personal data, for example, if:

they are no longer needed for the original processing purposes;

consent has been used as a legal basis for their processing;

there is no legitimate interest for the further processing of personal data;

they were used for marketing purposes.

 

Right to restriction of processing

You can request us to suspend the processing of all or some of your personal data, for example, if your personal data are inaccurate or you believe that they are being processed illegally.

 

Right to data portability

You can request us to provide you with a copy of your personal data in machine-readable format (e.g. xml, csv) provided by you earlier.

 

Right to object

You can ask us to stop using your personal data for direct marketing purposes.
